Package: sanitizr
Title: Package to clean the workspace in an R session
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Holger", "Hoefling", email = "hhoeflin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package cleans the workspace of an R session by removing items in the 
	     global environment, detaches items on the search path, detaches attached packages
	     and unloads namespaces
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    tools
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    testthat,
    RColorBrewer
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
URL: https://github.com/hhoeflin/sanitizr
BugReports: https://github.com/hhoeflin/sanitizr/issues
